            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_12wh' title='Col. 12WH &mdash; HC Deb 05 March 2002 vol 381 c12WH' name='column_12wh' href='#column_12wh' rel='bookmark'>12WH</a>
            organisations participating, for example, in its guidelines-development process. Thereby, funds would not go from the charitable sector to the statutory sector on such a profligate basis.
          </p>
